  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Two suspects with drugs worth two crores",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Peliyagoda Mulasthan Police say that three suspects who were ready to transport cocaine, kush and ash worth nearly 2 crore rupees in a three-wheeler and a jeep were arrested.",
        "The police said that they tried to bribe the arrested suspects to the extent of 30 lakh rupees by carrying out the raid and asking them to release them without enforcing the law.",
        "According to the police, the suspects had 1 kg of cocaine, 24 kg and 500 grams of ash and 8 kg of kush.",
        "According to the information received by the Peliyagoda Police that some suspicious items were being loaded in a three-wheeler and a jeep on the Negombo road this morning, a police team went to the place this morning and found the above cargo during inspection.",
        "The police said that the drug was packed in three cardboard boxes and four large suitcases."
      ],
